<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>.. عَلاهَا ظَلامٌ لِلْبَلَى وَلَطَالَمَا<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>غَدًا نُورُهَا فِي حِنْدسِ الظُّلْمِ يَلْمَعُ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>كَأَنَّ لَمْ يَكُنْ يَوْمًا عَلا مِفْرقًا لَهَا<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>نَفَائِسُ تِيجَانٍ وَدُرٍّ مُرَصَّعُ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>تَبَاعَدَ عَنْهُمْ وَحْشَةً كُلُّ وَامِقٍ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>وَعَافَهُمْ الأَهْلُونَ وَالنَّاسُ أَجْمَعُ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>وَقَاطَعَهُمْ مَنْ كَانَ حَالَ حَيَاتِهِ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>بِوَصْلِهِمْ وِجْدًا بِهِمْ لَيْسَ يَطْمَعُ<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>يَبْكِيهِمْ الأَعْدَاءُ مِنْ سُوءِ حَالِهِمْ<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>وَيَرْحَمُهُمْ مَنْ كَانَ ضِدًّا وَيَجْزَعُ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>فَقُلْ لِلَّذِي قَدْ غَرَّهُ طُولُ عُمْرِهِ<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>وَمَا قَدْ حَوَاهُ مِنْ زَخَارِفٍ تَخْدَعُ<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>أَفِقْ وَانْظُرُ الدُّنْيَا بِعَيْنٍ بَصِيرَةٍ<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>تَجِدُ كَلَّ مَا فِيهَا وَدَائِعُ تَرْجِعُ<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>فَأَيْنَ الْمُلُوكَ الصَّيْد قَدْمًا وَمَنْ حَوَى<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>مِنَ الأَرْضِ مَا كَانَتِ بِهِ الشَّمْسُ تَطْلَعُ<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>حَوَاه ضَرِيحٌ مِنْ فَضَاءِ بَسِيطِهَا<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>يَقْصُرُ عَنْ جُثْمَانِهِ حِينَ يَذْرَعُ<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>فَكَمْ مَلِكْ أَضْحَى بِهَا ذَا مَذَلَّةٍ<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>وَقَدْ كَانَ حَيًّا لِلْمَهَابَةِ يُتْبَعُ<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>يَقُودُ عَلَى الْخَيْلِ الْعِتَاقِ فَوَارِسًا<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p22"></span>يَسُدُّ بِهَا رَحْبَ الْفَيَافِي وَيُتْرَعُ<a href="#p22" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>